title: Trendomatic For The People 10/20: Jeffrey Toobin, Space Jam 2, Pat Robertson, Ice Cube/50 Cent
itunes:title: Trendomatic For The People 10/20: Jeffrey Toobin, Space Jam 2, Pat Robertson, Ice Cube/50 Cent
description:
On this edition of Trendomatic For The People Jack and Miles discuss more details in the Jeffrey Toobin situation, the plot of Space Jam 2 leaked, Pat Robertson is doomsaying around Trump getting reelected, and a photo of Ice Cube and 50 Cent was photoshopped to make them look like Trump supporters.
